---
title: Creamy Tex-Mex Chicken & Bacon Potato Top Pie with Hidden Veggies & Corn
description: Turn a juicy chicken drizzled in a creamy corn and veggie sauce into a veggie, bacon and chicken pie, topped with potato. You can smell the Tex-Mex seasoning coming off the pie as it bakes, that’s when dinner gets very exciting, so dig in and enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/648bc2d1486bdf1babe821a5-b738fffe.jpeg
